title: Liquid Lipstick (Kathryn)
description:
Liquid Lipstick by Anastasia Beverly Hills is a full-pigment liquid lip colour formula that dries down to a weightless matte finish for smudge-proof wearability and long-lasting colour. This comfortable matte formula delivers full coverage wear and creates the appearance of fuller lips. 
 
Benefits: 
 
  Features a double-sided flat applicator with a rounded tip that distributes the perfect amount of product for precise application 
  The long-wearing shades are versatile enough for customisation, so you can mix and match multiple shades without losing pigment 
 
Features: 
 
  Cruelty-free 
  Vegan

title: Moisture Surge™ Overnight Mask
description:
A creamy, oil-free facial mask deeply nourishes and hydrates while you sleep. Leaves skin soft, dewy, glowing. 
 
 
 
 
 
Skin Type: Very Dry to Dry, Dry Combination, Combination Oily, Oily, Normal 
What It Does 
Did you know skin loses moisture while you sleep? This rich, penetrating night mask replenishes all night long. It soothes and nourishes to help the skin stay hydrated. You’ll wake up to soft, dewy, glowing skin. Recommended for all skin types. Oil-Free. Non-Acnegenic. Ophthalmologist Tested.

title: Easy Bake Loose Baking & Setting Powder (Kunafa)
description:
The Huda Beauty Easy Bake Loose Powders are inspired by Huda’s strong belief that the technique of baking is a key step to a flawless finish while ensuring long-lasting, melt-proof makeup. This extremely light and silky texture blends seamlessly into the skin leaving it matte with a hint of sheen, for a luminous finish that controls shine throughout the day. The powders work to subtly colour correct and highlight different contours of the face, leaving a translucent veil of colour on your skin. Huda Beauty's Easy Bake Loose Baking & Setting Powder are easy to use loose powder with a long-lasting complexion while blurring the appearance of pores and fine lines and holding makeup in place all day long. 
 
• Matte, luminous finish 
• Unique powder net to control product waste 
• Ultra-refined lightweight pigments

title: Kayali Vanilla | 28 Hand Cream
description:
A super nourishing, fast-absorbing hand cream enriched with skin-conditioning ingredients and scented with the essence of Kayali’s cult-fave fragrance, Vanilla | 28! 
 
Fragrance notes: Vanilla orchid, tonka absolute, brown sugar, amber woods, musk 
 
A warm and spicy vanilla bliss, the luxuriously silky formula nourishes the skin without feeling greasy or heavy! The enriching ingredients of safflower and sunflower oils, rosemary and ginseng soothe and condition hands, which is a life saver for stripped, dry skin that needs a surge of moisture! 
 
Key ingredients: 
 
Safflower & sunflower oils: 
Natural humectants provide nourishment to the skin, leaving you with silky soft hands. 
 
Ginseng: 
Used in herbal medicines for centuries, this antioxidant-rich ingredient soothes and calms. 
 
Rosemary leaf: 
Helps to reduce redness leaving you with calm and soothed skin. 
 
*Please note this hand cream is made with natural vanilla so the colour will evolve.
product_type: Bath & Body, Body Care, Hand Cream, Sale

title: Morphe x James Charles Eyeshadow Palette (Small)
description:
The colour never ends with this full spectrum of 39 dialled-up, deeply pigmented shades. With four rows of stunning colour combos and one row of super-sized shades, you’ll be ready to take on any look you can dream up. 
 
Shades: 
 
  Row 1: Canvas (matte cream), Ringlight (shimmer pearl), So Good (metallic true gold), 518 (matte neon orange), Rusted (matte chilli orange), Halloween (metallic copper), Wig (metallic warm brass), Tea (matte dark taupe) 
  Row 2: Punch Me (matte latte), Sister (shimmer rose gold), Mary (matte dusty rose), Literally (shimmer flamingo pink), You're Kidding (matte red), Shook (metallic cranberry), Boutique (matte maroon), Benny (matte black coffee) 
  Row 3: Flashback (matte true white), Face (shimmer champagne highlight), Tune (matte light peach), Code James (matte sunset orange), 10% Off (matte burnt orange), No Beans (matte warm brown), Spooky (matte true black) 
  Row 4: Bee (matte bright yellow), Guac (metallic avocado green), Hello (shimmer blue ice), Playground (matte neon blue), Brother (matte true blue), Artistry (metallic amethyst purple), Love That (matte magenta), Pinkity Drinkity (matte baby pink) 
  Row 5: Social Blade (matte lime green), Daddy (matte forest green), Cape Cod (metallic seafoam blue), Cola (matte royal blue), A Cappella (metallic navy blue), Escape (matte plum purple), Single (matte orchid purple), Skip (matte neon pink)

title: #FauxFilter Skin Finish Buildable Coverage Foundation Stick (Chai 210B)
description:
The luxuriously creamy stick formula melts into the skin for a natural filtered finish that lasts up to 10 hours. Whether you prefer full coverage or barely any at all, this versatile formula will let you be the master of your complexion. Swipe it on and build it up, the stick formula is ideal if you’re on the go or in a hurry, and thanks to its long-wearing, waterproof, humidity and sweat-resistant formula, you can set it and forget it for the rest of the day. 
 
Formula: Stick (Cream) 
Coverage: Customizable (Light/Buildable) 
Finish: Natural 
 
Fragrance-free, Vegan, Non-Comedogenic, Water-proof, 10-Hour-Wear

title: Wishful Quench Skincare Kit
description:
Skin Type: Combination, Dry, Normal, Oily 
Skin Concerns: Dryness, Dullness 
Formulation: Sheet 
How to Use:  
 
 
  Thirst Trap Sheet Mask: start with clean, dry skin. Remove the protective film from the mask. Apply to dry face and leave for 20 minutes. Remove and gently pat excess formula into the skin. 
* Chin Lift: starting with a clean and dry face, peel the protective film from the mask. Tug on each end to pre-stretch the mask to avoid any discomfort during use. Starting at the chin and pulling upwards, secure the mask around the ears. Leave for 20-30 minutes (or longer for even more lift and enhancement of the jawline).
product_type: Mask & Serum, Sets & Gifts, Sheet Mask, Skin Care

title: Wishful Glow Skincare Kit
description:
Skin Type: Combination, Dry, Normal, Oily, Sensitive 
Skin Concerns: Blemishes, Dryness, Dullness, Uneven Skin Texture, Visible Pores 
How to Use:  
 
 
  Yo Glow: Apply a generous amount on clean, dry skin. Gently massage the scrub in circular motions across the face and neck, rolling and sweeping away dead skin cells and impurities. Rinse well with warm water and gently pat the skin dry. For all skin types, it is recommended that you use Yo Glow 1-2 times a week. However, if you don’t have sensitive skin it’s suitable to be used every day. 
  Honey Balm: Apply a generous amount on clean dry skin. Gently massage into skin, taking in the relaxing lavender scent. Use twice a day for best effects.

title: Moisture Surge™ Intense 72H Lipid-Replenishing Hydrator
description:
Rich cream-gel delivers 72-hour hydration for velvety-smooth skin. Tested in Siberiaand the results were glowing. 
 
 
 
 
 
Skin Type: Very Dry to Dry, Dry Combination 
What It Does 
Our richest formula yet sets non-stop hydration into motion with the help of activated aloe water and caffeine. Then locks it in with a trio of lipids, strengthening the skin’s barrier to keep moisture in and helps keep aggressors out. Keeps skin hydrated for 72 hours, leaving it glowing, plump, and velvety smooth. Calming circa helps soothe and comfort dry or dehydrated skin.

title: Moisture Surge™ 100H Auto-Replenishing Hydrator
description:
Refreshing oil-free gel-cream penetrates deep, lasts 100 hours. Locks in moisture for an endlessly plump, dewy glow. 
 
Skin Type: All Types of Skin 
 
Formula Facts 
 
  Oil-free 
  Dermatologist tested 
  Fragrance-free 
  Allergy tested 
 
Free Of 
Paraben-free, Phthalate-free, Fragrance-free, Oil-free, Alcohol-free 
What It Does 
 
  Many things can dehydrate your skin, including weather, pollution, blue light, time spent in the sun, mask-wearing, air travel, air conditioning, and heating. 
  Fight back against life’s daily dehydrations. This oil-free gel-cream moisturizer with Aloe Bioferment + HA Complex penetrates deep into the skin’s surface—for 100 hours of stabilizing hydration. 
  Plus, Auto-Replenishing Technology helps skin create its own internal water source to continually rehydrate itself, then locks in moisture. 
  Skin feels soothed with hydration in 3 seconds, and it keeps on glowing. 
  Provides a smooth canvas for makeup application. 
  For mask wearers, Moisture Surge™ 100H is truly a moisture marvel. It’s proven to help prevent drying and barrier damage from prolonged mask-wearing when applied 3x/day for 7 days (compared to masked skin without Moisture Surge™ 100H).

title: Vitamin C Suspension 30% in Silicone
description: Vitamin C is an effective antioxidant that brightens the skin tone and reduces the appearance of signs of aging. This water-free formula provides 30% pure L-Ascorbic Acid which remains completely stable due to the absence of water. Due to the presence of very light silicones, this formulation feels smooth on the skin despite the suspension format of the formulation, avoiding the short-lived gritty feeling of our original Vitamin C Suspension 23% + HA Spheres 2% formula. This treatment is ideally applied at bedtime. It contains an extra-strong Vitamin C serum which helps to brighten skin and reduce the signs of aging.

description:

description: Anastasia Beverly Hills Loose Pigment is a finely milled, shimmering loose powder pigment for eyes, face, and body that delivers a pearlescent metallic finish. description:

title: Alyssa Edwards Eyeshadow Palette (Limited Edition)
description: Alyssa Edwards Eyeshadow Palette is a limited-edition palette that features mostly mattes in a mix of vibrant hues and grounding neutrals. Per the box, the following shades are Pressed Pigments, which is code for “not intended for use around the immediate eye area.” Those shades are Texas Made, Dream It, BBDC, and Believe. I did get moderate staining with those shades, which lingered beyond my morning cleanse, and I did get staining even when I wore it over an eyeshadow primer, though a thicker primer might prevent it. Most shades were pigmented, but they often took more effort to blend, while two of three shimmers were let downs.

title: DipBrow Pomade (Chocolate)
description:
DipBrow Pomade by Anastasia Beverly Hills is a highly pigmented brow gel featuring a long-lasting, waterproof formula for creating fuller-looking, defined brows. The unique formula adheres to brow hairs, builds the appearance of fullness, and dries down to a seamless matte finish. 
 
Benefits: 
 
  Long-wearing, smudge-resistant, waterproof formula 
  The creamy texture is easy to pick up on the brush, glides on smoothly to the skin and hair, adheres without building too much, and blends out for a natural-looking finish 
  Allows for versatility in application, giving you the artistic ability to create everything from natural-looking hairs to bold outlining and filling 
  A highly pigmented formula mimics the hairlike texture, making it ideal for creating hair where it is sparse or adding volume to hair that already exists 
  Although waterproof, the formula allows time for blending before drying to a matte finish 
 
Features: 
 
  Cruelty-free 
  Vegan

description:
Matte Lipstick by Anastasia Beverly Hills is a full-pigment lip colour with a velvety-smooth ultra-matte finish and comfortable wearability. Available in a wide range of neutrals, bolds and bright accent shades, its heart-shaped bullet delivers ultimate control for a precise colour application. 
 
Benefits: 
 
  The easy-to-apply, full-pigment formula delivers an ultra-matte finish that seamlessly glides on the lips 
  The collection includes a wide range of neutral tones, bright accent shades and bold colours 
  The shade range includes a selection of nude shades that complement every skin tone and undertone 
  The precise heart-shaped bullet provides excellent control for defining the lip line and effortlessly creating a long-lasting application

  Vegan

description:
Liquid Lipstick by Anastasia Beverly Hills is a full-pigment liquid lip colour formula that dries down to a weightless matte finish for smudge-proof wearability and long-lasting colour. This comfortable matte formula delivers full coverage wear and creates the appearance of fuller lips.

description:

title: Hydrating Milky Serum
description:
A revitalising boost for the skin that intensely hydrates and protects while improving elasticity. This nutrient-rich serum restores dehydrated skin, revealing its natural radiance. Silky-smooth and lightweight, this serum gives a burst of hydration without a heavy feel. Rose flower extract, jojoba oil and Aloe Vera nourish the skin while glycerin traps moisture for a plumped effect. 
 
Benefits:  
• Suited for all skin types 
• Not tested on animals 
• Paraben-free

title: Overnight Glow Serum
description:
A concentrated exfoliating gel that helps to reveal a more even & radiant skin tone overnight. A serum that works while you sleep to exfoliate and soothe skin for a brighter complexion in the morning. Sleep off fatigued and stressed skin with the Overnight Glow Serum by Pixi. The potent serum helps to reduce the appearance of fine lines and fade sun spots over time with a nutrient-rich formula including calming cucumber and aloe vera extracts, as well as nourishing vitamins A, C and E. It exfoliates & soothes skin with this miracle serum that works while you sleep to reveal a brighter complexion. 
 
Benefits: 
• Formulated with 10% Glycolic Acid & Arginine. 
• Helps to reduce the appearance of fine lines and fade sun spots over time. 
• Enriched with Cucumber & Aloe Vera extracts to calm skin. 
• Vitamins A, C & E to nourish 
• Suited on all skin types 
• Not tested on animals 
• Paraben-free

title: Vitamin C Serum
description:
Vitamin C Serum provides brightening and Antioxidants to the skin for a boost of both immediate and long-term radiance. Vitamin C Serum provides a radiant glow. This enriching serum helps improve skin tone and creates a smoother complexion while reducing the effects of sun damage and free radicals. Vitamin-C Serum includes the promotion of healthy collagen production as well as a noticeable boost in the skin's natural luminosity. It creates a smoother complexion by improving the appearance of skin tone. 
 
Benefits: 
• Skin is soothed and hydrated with added Aloe Extract. 
• Formulated with Lemon, Orange and Grapefruit Extracts. 
• Suitable for all skin types 
• Paraben-free 
• Not tested on animals

title: Dramatically Different Hydrating Jelly Anti Pollution
description:
Lightweight water-jelly face moisturizer delivers 24-hour hydration repair plus pollution protection. 
 
Skin Type: All Types of Skin 
 
Key Ingredients: 
Clean Shield Technology™ is formulated with a moisture barrier blend of sunflower seed cake, barley extract and cucumber fruit extract to strengthen the skin’s barrier, improve its resiliency, and balance and retain skin’s moisture levels. Hyaluronic acid acts as a natural moisture magnet/humectant. 
 
What It Does:  
24-hour hydrator with Clean Shield Technology™ locks in the good like moisture and filters out the bad. 
Strengthens skin’s moisture barrier and improves resiliency. 
The unique water-jelly texture feels fresh, penetrates quickly. 
Oil-free formula is non-sticky, leaves no residue. 
Skin is smooth, strong and healthy with a pure, clean glow.
